com.hcl.domino.data

Interface DominoCollection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DominoClientDescendant, IAdaptable

    public interface DominoCollection
extends IAdaptable, DominoClientDescendant
    Term borrowed from MongoDB. Covers Domino views/folders Collection Type (static = view) Contains CollectionEntry, Hibernate compliant

      • getAllIds

        Set<Integer> getAllIds(boolean withDocuments,
                       boolean withCategories)
        Returns an ordered set of note ids for collection entries that the current user is allowed to see.

        Implementations are likely, but not guaranteed, to return a LinkedHashSet.

        Parameters:
        withDocuments - true to return document note ids
        withCategories - true to return category note ids
        Returns:
        sorted set of note ids

      • getAllIdsByKey

        Set<Integer> getAllIdsByKey(Set<Find> findFlags,
                            Object key)
        Returns an ordered set of note ids for collection entries that match the specified lookup key

        Implementations are likely, but not guaranteed, to return a LinkedHashSet.

        Parameters:
        findFlags - flags to configure the lookup operation
        key - lookup key (String, Number, DominoDateRange)
        Returns:
        sorted set of note ids

      • getAllIdsByKey

        Set<Integer> getAllIdsByKey(Set<Find> findFlags,
                            Collection<Object> key)
        Returns an ordered set of note ids for collection entries that match the specified lookup key (supporting multi column lookups)

        Implementations are likely, but not guaranteed, to return a LinkedHashSet.

        Parameters:
        findFlags - flags to configure the lookup operation
        key - lookup key (list of String, Number, DominoDateRange)
        Returns:
        sorted set of note ids
